'''Patricia C. Wrede''' (born [[March 27]], [[1950s#1953|1953]]) is the author of the junior novelizations of the [[Star Wars]] [[Prequel trilogy]]. She is a children's science fiction and fantasy author.

Patricia Wrede currently lives in Minneapolis, Minnesota.

